{"tid":227301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動物團體人士網上聯署　轟馬會人道毁滅受傷馬匹","createTime":"2017-05-03T05:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T12:28:05.000Z","uid":319,"like":3,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8abde656d21c27e83c6897e64b45f99f67bffb78","tid":227301,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170502/s00001/e7a961a8cf0adf0d853b1bc3d176dedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2Fe7a961a8cf0adf0d853b1bc3d176dedb.jpg&h=d311c7e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田馬場上月賽馬發生墮馬事件，3歲馬「飛鶯」左前腳折斷，被當場人道毁滅，有關注動物權益團體人士翻查馬會資料，指從2014至2016年，至少有28匹馬遭人道毁滅或暴斃，當中絕大部分喺賽事中意外斷腳，或因操練過度而死亡。團體人士今日喺網上發起聯署行動，要求馬會善待馬匹，甚至長遠應取締賽馬活動。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信要求，馬會應訂立因訓練或比賽而令馬受傷嘅罰則，例如需停賽或罰款等，以阻嚇過度操練馬匹嘅練馬師；又指最終希望可全面取締賽馬活動，因為賽馬屬殘忍運動。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信引述動保團體PETA嘅報告，話賽馬業界繁殖者會針對賽馬配種出跑速快嘅馬，但呢啲馬嘅四肢往往會過幼，有較高折斷風險。該信又批評，當馬受傷，對練馬師同馬主再無利用價值，於是就用「乾淨快捷」嘅「人道毁滅」方法處理。<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會回應指，一直致力保障馬嘅健康和福祉，聘用數百名受過專業訓練嘅員工，專責為馬提供最高水平嘅護理同照料。對於會唔會停止人道毁滅，或要求馬主照料馬匹一世，馬會無就此回應。馬會話喺每場賽事前後，獸醫同醫生團隊均會密切監察，以確保參賽馬可以喺最短時間內獲得適當護理支援。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170502/s00001/1493733382506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2F1493733382506&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8ef01dce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170502%2Fs00001%2F1493733382506&h=8ab1cf42\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170502/s00001/1493733382506</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a8a7e6fff3eed8ffeaeaa984d4b70d4dafb5fa","tid":227301,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"動物團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102280a808b68d2f6ab9e0c4c1950dfafb87627c","tid":227301,"uid":22926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"連登班動物台應該要去反啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdad4ecfd5020bcac71a4520ed7717e8fab86917","tid":227301,"uid":71728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"一邊鋸牛扒 一邊咬雞髀 係度叫人唔好殺馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c9294c04462af23646fe9e0c6a5c8844affa10","tid":227301,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一邊鋸牛扒 一邊咬雞髀 係度叫人唔好殺馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa002e536e7cc7a203c07ec5dae6d99fc9fed883","tid":227301,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"e6191d8f54d9e87f72debd64942fc2708671fd89","tid":227301,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"其實無錯,跑馬真係有錢人既殘酷遊戲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n斷腳即啪,佢地會唔會傷心?跌左錢果種傷心就會,會關心隻馬?屌柒個練馬師就有份"},{"pid":"4717f1045a5043e910b00ec3809276c86ffce708","tid":227301,"uid":59684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/03/135148_1f7ffa8bd1200a8c00530e86a3ed7d1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F